snippet.title: Tonari no Princess Rolfee! Gameplay
snippet.description: I play 15 min of the NEC PC-FX game Tonari no Princess Rolfee. This is an adventure/life simulation style game featuring the PC-FX mascot Rolfee. Enjoy!
